# Netlify _redirects for SPA routing
# CRITICAL: Explicit identity rules for static files BEFORE the wildcard!
# The 200! (with bang) forces serve-as-is even with SPA routing.

# SEO files - must serve as static
/robots.txt /robots.txt 200!
/sitemap.xml /sitemap.xml 200!

# Agent discovery
/.well-known/* /.well-known/:splat 200!

# SPA fallback - MUST BE LAST
/* /index.html 200
